task.summary: Avoid multiple queries to the activity preference database at startup.
Tinted status bar on API>=19, underline color changed to white at search view
Added overflow menu to the action bar, code cleanup
Fix compatibility with some devices (app was broken on Gingerbread)
Updated screenshots, correct Material Status Bar Color @ API21+
Fix About activity status bar color on Lollipop+
Delete entries from app preference database if the app is not found at startup
Trim text box content before searching.
Trie: Using HashSet to avoid returning duplicates on method getAllStartingWith
changed return type of getAllStartingWith to HashSet
